column1:
"Okay! Based on your message, I can help you with that. Here are the three values I extract from your message:

1. frequenza (you want to know your heart rate frequency)
2. lista (you want a list of all your heart rate readings)
3. grafico (you want to see a graphical representation of your heart rate data)

So, your request can be summarized as: frequenza lista grafico." "FREQUENZA -1 LISTA"
